                "SISD",
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Charged reaction products were detected",
                "by means of the three delta E-E telescopes of the DINEX",
                "Each telescope was composed of two double-sided silicon",
                "strip detectors-DSSSDs, with thicknesses of 40-42 and",
                "1000 mum for the delta-E and E-res layers,respectively.",
                "Each DSSSD had an active area of 50*50 mm**2 and the",
                "detector front and back sides were both segmented into",
                "16 strips in order to define a pixel structure with 256",
                "elements of approx. 9 mm**2 area."
              ]
            }
